edu.wpi.grip.core.operations.network.networktables

Class NTPublishAnnotatedOperation<S,T extends Publishable,P>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.grip.core.operations.network.PublishOperation<S,MapNetworkPublisher<P>>
      • edu.wpi.grip.core.operations.network.PublishAnnotatedOperation<S,T,P>
        • edu.wpi.grip.core.operations.network.networktables.NTPublishAnnotatedOperation<S,T,P>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Operation

    public abstract class NTPublishAnnotatedOperation<S,T extends Publishable,P>
extends PublishAnnotatedOperation<S,T,P>
    An operation that publishes any type that implements Publishable to NetworkTables.

    To be publishable, a type should have one or more accessor methods annotated with PublishValue. This is done with annotations instead of methods
